Package: ReMIXTURE
Title: ReMIXTURE
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("M Timothy", "Rabanus-Wallace", , "mtrw85@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: M Timothy Rabanus-Wallace <mtrw85@gmail.com>
Description: 
    Implementation of the ReMIXTURE method to quantify how (genetic or other) diversity is distributed and shared between regional groups, and to create pretty and intuitive plots showing this on a globe.
    Evolved from the idea originally published in Tripodi & Rabanus-Wallace, et al.,2021 (10.1073/pnas.2104315118).
License: GPL-3
